== 註解 ==
*{{note label|a|a|a}} 預計取消資格因為2016年6月17日宣布重新藥檢呈現陽性。[[國際奧委會|國際奧委會]]宣布將由[[國際舉重總會|國際舉重總會]]處理。<ref name="IWF18June">{{cite news|title=PUBLIC DISCLOSURES|url=http://www.iwf.net/2016/06/18/public-disclosures-2/|work=IWF|date=18 June 2016|accessdate=2016-10-02|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630043712/http://www.iwf.net/2016/06/18/public-disclosures-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*{{note label|a|b|b}} [[西貝爾·厄茲坎|西貝爾·厄茲坎]] (TUR) 被取消資格因為違反禁藥規定。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-sanctions-turkish-weightlifter-for-failing-anti-doping-test-at-beijing-2008 |title=IOC sanctions Turkish weightlifter for failing anti-doping test at Beijing 2008 |accessdate=2016-10-02 |archive-date=2017-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905142459/https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-sanctions-turkish-weightlifter-for-failing-anti-doping-test-at-beijing-2008 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*{{note label|c|c|c}} 預計取消資格因為2016年8月24日宣布重新藥檢呈現陽性。[[國際奧委會|國際奧委會]]宣布將由[[國際舉重總會|國際舉重總會]]處理。<ref name="IWF24August">{{Cite web |url=http://summergames.ap.org/article/3-olympic-weightlifting-gold-medalists-fail-doping-retests |title=3 Olympic weightlifting gold medalists fail doping retests<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |access-date=2016-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160929232322/http://summergames.ap.org/article/3-olympic-weightlifting-gold-medalists-fail-doping-retests |archive-date=2016-09-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

